snippet.textDisplay:
When Ahmed says "Rabb-e-Zarb-e-Haider o Hamza bhi tu" I get goosebumps everytime..!
We can't get naseehat from authentic sources but this.. this is emotional! How grand those personalities would be?! Syed us Shuhdaa Hazrat Hamza A.S and on the other hand, we literally have Asad Ullah (Lion of God). If this is the grandeour of these personalities, mere mortals, then what would be the Grandness of their Creator and their Maula?! I get goosebumps literally everytime thinking about this.
May Allah guide him to the Siraat-e-Mustaqim ❤😊
